 Here is the complete, high-quality, responsive, and accessible institutional website code for **Epower Minds**.

This is a **Single Page Application (SPA)**. It includes all 12 requested pages/sections, a global contact modal, three distinct forms with client-side validation and localStorage integration, interactive SVG diagrams, and full compliance with LGPD and accessibility standards.

